                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18190421-59-off338 t18190421-59-crimeloc340"></join>, and felt something at my pocket; I turned round, and collared the prisoner with my handkerchief in his hand. He threw it down, and I gave him in charge - two or three others were with him.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
